c: 6
v: 108
t: "Oo ha caayina kuwaa ay u dhawaaqdaan Allaah sokadi, si aysan iyagoo xadgudbaya markaa u caayin Allaah jahli darti. Sidaas baan ugu qurxinnay ummad walba camalkeeda (khayr ama shar midkay doortaan); markaas waa xagga Rabbigood meel noqodkoodu, markaas wuxuu u sheegi doonaa waxa ay fali jireen"